  "response": "Here are some useful Facebook tips and hacks:\n\n1. Privacy and Security Tips:\n- Use two-factor authentication\n- Limit who can see your posts\n- Review your privacy settings regularly\n- Control tagging permissions\n- Use privacy checkup tool\n\n2. Posting Tips:\n- Use best times to post for more engagement\n- Use hashtags strategically\n- Schedule posts in advance\n- Add alt text to images for accessibility\n\n3. Profile Management:\n- Hide/archive old posts\n- Create friend lists for selective sharing\n- Turn off message read receipts\n- Download a copy of your Facebook data\n- Unfollow instead of unfriending\n\n4. Useful Features:\n- Use Facebook Marketplace\n- Create/join groups\n- Use Facebook Watch\n- Try Facebook Dating\n- Use Facebook Messenger features\n\n5. Productivity Hacks:\n- Use Facebook saved links\n- Create/use shortcuts\n- Use Facebook news feed preferences\n- Manage notifications effectively\n- Use Facebook's dark mode\n\n6. Content Tips:\n- Use Facebook Live\n- Create photo/video albums\n- Use reactions beyond likes\n- Try Facebook Stories\n- Use Facebook's built-in photo editing tools\n\nRemember to always prioritize your privacy and be cautious about sharing personal information online.",
